London Queens Club

Alcaraz, Fearnley advance on Thursday

June 19, 2025

Luke Walker/Getty Images for LTA

Andy Murray Arena is centre court at Queen's Club in London. By ATP Staff

The action continued on Thursday at the HSBC Championships, where Carlos Alcaraz and Jacob Fearnley rallied for three-set victories.

View all of Thursday's results from the ATP 500 event held at Queen's Club below.
